From 3817e968f2d9d58f4048812034d225b69f6d8499 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Sushant Butta <sbutta@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Tue, 1 Jul 2025 00:43:16 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 4/6] UPSTREAM: DP: wifi: ath12k: Refactor WCN7850 Destination
 Ring Handling to dp_mon1.c

WCN785 destination ring processing is currently part of ath12k/dp_mon.c
(ath12k.ko common module) with the Unified Driver framework,
WCN7850 adopts the monitor quad ring model (mon1), so the destination ring
processing logic is being moved to the architecture-specific file
ath12k/wifi7/dp_mon1.c(ath12k_wifi7.ko arch specific module)

Patch-dependency:
	0404-0003-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-Refactor-WCN7850-Status-Ring.patch

Signed-off-by: Sushant Butta <sbutta@qti.qualcomm.com>
